OL,4,CBelfast Council flag dispute
OL,6,FBelfast City Council is "piling
OL,7,Fillegality on illegality" in its
OL,8,Fprocess for dealing with a proposed
OL,9,FIrish language policy, the High Court
OL,10,Fheard on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe local authority's rules on
OL,13,Freconsidering politically divisive
OL,14,Fdecisions about both the planned
OL,15,Fstrategy and flying of the Palestinian
OL,16,Fflag unlawfully undermines safeguards
OL,17,Faimed at protecting minority views, a
OL,18,Fjudge was told.
