OL,4,CBelfast Council flag dispute
OL,6,FTraditional Unionist Voice (TUV)
OL,7,Fmember Ann McClure is challenging the
OL,8,FCouncil over the operation of a call-
OL,9,Fin scheme for voting on controversial
OL,10,Fissues with a potential adverse
OL,11,Fcommunity impact.
OL,13,FIt's alleged
OL,15,FHer barrister, John Larkin KC, argued
OL,16,Fa new filter has now wrongly been
OL,17,Fcreated, handing a veto to a simple
OL,18,Fmajority of the elected
OL,19,Frepresentatives.
