OL,6,F"The standing orders haven't been
OL,7,Fremoved or suspended... it is piling
OL,8,Fillegality on illegality," he
OL,9,Fsubmitted.
OL,11,FProceedings were issued after
OL,12,Fcouncillors in Belfast approved a
OL,13,Fdraft Irish language policy in October
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FThe blueprint aims to promote the use
OL,17,Fof Irish in public life, with
OL,18,Fbilingual signage and logos to appear
OL,19,Fon council facilities, signage and
OL,20,Funiforms.
