OL,6,FThe draft Irish language policy for
OL,7,FBelfast currently remains on hold
OL,8,Fpending the outcome of that process.
OL,10,FMs McClure and her legal team claim
OL,11,Fthe Council has wrongly interpreted
OL,12,Frelevant sections of the Local
OL,13,FGovernment (Northern Ireland) Act 2014.
OL,15,FHer action widened out into a systemic
OL,16,Fchallenge after the authority backed a
OL,17,FSinn Fein proposal to fly the
OL,18,FPalestinian flag for one day at City
OL,19,FHall.
