OL,6,FUnionists again objected and called in
OL,7,Fthe original decision taken to mark
OL,8,FPalestinian Solidarity Day.
OL,10,FFollowing a further vote the flag was
OL,11,Feventually raised for a short period
OL,12,Fat the start of December.
OL,14,FCourt papers described Ms McClure as a
OL,15,Fpolitically active member of the
OL,16,Funionist community in Belfast who has
OL,17,Factively campaigned against the
OL,18,Fadoption and implementation of an
OL,19,FIrish language policy.
