OL,6,F"What is the value in obtaining
OL,7,F(legal) opinion on matters of
OL,8,Fsociology and politics?" Mr Larkin
OL,9,Fasked.
OL,11,FHe went on: "By the simple majority
OL,12,FBelfast City Council is introducing a
OL,13,Ffilter... depriving councillors and
OL,14,Fthose people whose interests they
OL,15,Frepresent, of the protections the
OL,16,Fregulations give to them."
